      "title": "DLP policies by enforcement mode",
      "description": "\n\nNeeds a **Loki** datasource (selected above). Log attributes are Loki *structured metadata*, not stream labels: filter with `| event_name=\u2026` after `{service_name=\"graph2otel\"}`. A stream selector on an attribute matches zero rows silently (#90).",
