          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {},
          "noValue": "No rows. Either no Loki datasource is selected above, or nothing matched. Log attributes are structured metadata: filter with | attr=\u2026 after {service_name=\"graph2otel\"}, never {attr=\"\u2026\"}."
